{"tid":1284082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要打持久戰的話，請加入警隊，民建聯，公務員","createTime":"2019-07-04T04:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T11:11:31.000Z","uid":268153,"like":12,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"161dc9d86700610cbefad61c4f942549c344c950","tid":1284082,"uid":268153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"分享巴打Rock Cheung 既留言<br />\n<br />\n首先，希望年青人不要灰心、氣餒！與其浪費青春十年八年於監獄，倒不如『忍辱負重』，投考警察、公務員！<br />\n您們都是社會的精英、未來的棟樑，不要說什麼督察、警司、AO&hellip;&hellip;等，甚至警務署長、局長、司長、特首都可以做到！<br />\n請記著：一百年前孫中山先生的辛亥革命，都是因為新軍內有大量支持革命之士；又或30年前的東歐『蘇東坡事件』，更是因為在蘇聯出了一個戈爾巴喬夫!<br />\n『身在曹營心在漢』，不要以為加入警隊就是叛徒，既然政權擁有絕大資源，大家就應該利用這資源&mdash;&mdash;打著紅旗反紅旗；表面是建制一員（跟區議員、立法會議員一樣），實際是支持改革的中流砥柱！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%94%A8%E8%A1%80%E8%82%89%E5%92%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%89%80%E7%AF%89%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%25A1%2580%25E8%2582%2589%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%2589%2580%25E7%25AF%2589%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%2F&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=828ac997\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E8%25A1%2580%25E8%2582%2589%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%2589%2580%25E7%25AF%2589%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%258B%2595%2F&h=181b9674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%94%A8%E8%A1%80%E8%82%89%E5%92%8C%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%89%80%E7%AF%89%E6%88%90%E7%9A%84%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95/</a>"},{"pid":"b909f9baa73458d5e756c0815231ffc33b680051","tid":1284082,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T04:22:47.000Z","msg":"同流合污？"},{"pid":"dc11307547bf018a8346